n扒類大部分都推既 因為來貨係高質的<br />\n唯一不推既係個最平既西冷<br />\n叫得就一定提d客硬到hihi<br />\nd客通常一聽到就會轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌首選一定係肉醬意粉<br />\n員工餐都有呢樣野簡<br />\n但我從來無食過就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好奇問下 員工餐有咩揀"},{"pid":"3e4cc3df6807c2935bea5f786e56972c3072e11b","tid":207133,"uid":90688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T09:59:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老老豆豆 厨房/厨房佬乾唔乾淨?</blockquote><br />\n我間分店識得既廚房加廚房佬都係乾淨既<br />\n自少係我接受到既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155219540fd606b68a75498d553a3cb919a5f7f9","tid":207133,"uid":57624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"毒撚唔敢去in 人工如何"},{"pid":"c207c11f22bb062e0426d2ccdc676fcff9346645","tid":207133,"uid":90688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有咩食推介？有咩係狗也不屌？</blockquote><br />\n扒類大部分都推既 因為來貨係高質的<br />\n唯一不推既係個最平既西冷<br />\n叫得就一定提d客硬到hihi<br />\nd客通常一聽到就會轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌首選一定係肉醬意粉<br />\n員工餐都有呢樣野簡<br />\n但我從來無食過就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好奇問下 員工餐有咩揀</blockquote><br />\n以前就係狗也不屌既肉醬意粉啊 一個雞既漢堡加薯條 沙律之類<br />\n後來比d員工屌9佢難食之後就轉左<br />\n加比密汁雞扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  豬扒飯啊 迷你漢堡等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2db04f919984d5f270d3cb04986a9f43b5d9bf6","tid":207133,"uid":90688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T10:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>毒撚唔敢去in 人工如何</blockquote><br />\n我2年前入42 做左1年到加到48 你唔出聲就會扮曬野唔加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正常有手有腳都會請 因為聽人講間間都唔夠人到hihi"}]}